<br>
I see many guilds having more than 1 person on the list, and i'm 100 % sure that those guilds already have some cleric epics.  I think there should be given a priority to guilds who don`t have an epic cleric.  <br>
<br>
Why ? Well, just see it this way, those guilds will get many, many epics, wich ain`t all that important to them.<br>
<br>
Some guilds have to wait 6 months to get their ragefire, and yet they don`t have 1 epic cleric yet.  for them having to wait 6 months is ... well, who knows if the cleric is ready to wait 6 months anyways.  <br>
<br>
